Run these steps on all the app servers

### 1. Install cronie and start crond

On each server:


sudo yum install -y cronie
sudo systemctl enable --now crond


(If the servers use `dnf`, replace `yum` with `dnf`.)

### 2. Add the root cron job

As root:
sudo crontab -l 2>/dev/null | { cat; echo "*/5 * * * * echo hello > /tmp/cron_text"; } | sudo crontab -


### 3. Verify
Check the cron entry:

sudo crontab -l

Expected output includes:

*/5 * * * * echo hello > /tmp/cron_text

Check the service:
systemctl status crond
